        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Emergency Support for Substance Use Disorders Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration to award grants to states, other jurisdictions, and community-based entities for harm reduction activities to address drug misuse during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
